      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WARREN'S LEDGER (4) flew the lids with a fast early split last time, hitting the frame with a 1.3 lengths third (22.01) over 390m at this track and making it two placings on end. Comes through a solid form race last start. Racing well and deserves a win. ZIPPING SMEE (6) is having his first start around this track. Comes here a last start placegetter at Nowra in a Grade 5 (20.91). Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Expected to be in this for a long way. OUR PATCH (1) finished well back at this track last time when a 6 length fifth (22.60) but recorded second best time of the card when winning four back. Has a good record here at this journey. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Should be about the money. SHALLOW SALLY (7) boasts a solid strike-rate from this box.",
